<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>I'm wondering why the guy who tries to sabotage the mission wants to forever destroy the prospects of the He3 motherload. Is he/she an anti-nuke activist?<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
